original: Kjellnäs, Carl Folke Vilhelm, drifts-ingenjör, Göteborg, f. 4/12/13 i Skärstad, Jönköp. 1. G. m. Inga Helander. Barn: Jan f. 38, Per 40, Stefan 43. — Utex. fr. Örebro tekn. gymn. Anst. v. Husqvarna Vapenfabr. A-B 30-31, Konfektioiis A-B Junex i Huskvarna 34-35, telegr:v. verkst. i Nynäshamn 35, Tornval’1’s Konfektions A-B i Södertälje 36-39, A-B J. A. Wet- tergren & Co. i Gbg sed. 39, drifts-ing. där. Stud:res. t. Tyskl. 38, USA 45-46. Led. av styr. f. Tekn. ’samf. avd. f. textiltekn. sed. 45, sekr. i Kon-fektionsinid. driftsled: fören. Skr.: art. i facktekn. tidskr. Hobby: tennis.
translated: Kjellnäs, Carl Folke Vilhelm, operating engineer, Gothenburg, b. 4/12/13 in Skärstad, Jönköp. 1. M. m. Inga Helander. Children: Jan b. 38, Per 40, Stefan 43. — Graduated from Örebro Technical Gymnasium. Employed by Husqvarna Vapenfabr. A-B 30-31, Konfektioiis A-B Junex in Huskvarna 34-35, telegraphist at Nynäshamn 35, Tornvall's Konfektions A-B in Södertälje 36-39, A-B J. A. Wettergren & Co. in Gothenburg since 39, operating engineer there. Studied abroad in Germany 38, USA 45-46. Member of the board of the Technical Society Department of Textile Technology since 45, secretary of the Clothing Industry Operating Management Association. Writings: articles in technical journals. Hobby: tennis.
